The Death Games Have Begun | Exiled: The Chosen Ones | Full Movie

After a man-made virus failed to reduce the population, global leaders start a game show. Random contestants are put into a concrete jungle and forced to kill each other. Viewers place their bets on who would win.

2022.  Stars: James Jaysen Bryhan, Carl Wharton, Sunny Pang
